\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \s42 \rtlch\fcs1 \af42\afs20\alang1037 \ltrch\fcs0 \f3\fs16\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8860867\charrsid2578727 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Only mark emails as important if they really are important.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \s42 \rtlch\fcs1 \af42\afs20\alang1037 \ltrch\fcs0 \f3\fs16\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8860867\charrsid2578727 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Ensure you send your email only to people who }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af42 
