\par Email has become an integral part of our
 digital lives today. There are a plethora of messaging apps available on the internet, many of which promise to redefine communication with the use of emojis, sticker packs, and a whole lot more. But no matter if you\rquote 
re an individual, team, group, or a large organization, email is something everyone uses.
