\par However, the volume of email that everyone has to process has increased exponentially over the last few years. An average internet user receives }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af42 \ltrch\fcs0 \f31506\insrsid1068553\charrsid2578727 many kinds of}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af42 
\ltrch\fcs0 \f31506\insrsid11800560\charrsid2578727  email, ranging from personal and work emails, period newsletters from the services they use, product updates from companies, offers and deals from online stores, and those occasional \'93}{\rtlch\fcs1 
