\b\i\f1\fs28\lang2057\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp2057\langfenp1033 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af42\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \i0\f31506\fs24\insrsid11800560\charrsid2578727 9. Email isn\rquote t Confidential
\par }\pard\plain \ltrpar\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid3687428 \rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs20\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp2057\langfenp1033 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af42 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f31506\insrsid11800560\charrsid2578727 Email is just a block of text that is transmitted from one computer to another. Any email can be accessed from any device, anywhere in the world. Keep this in mind when you\rquote 
re sharing any kind of content with someone via email. It\rquote s very easy to just forward that email to someone, or it \'93leaking\'94 within an organization (we\rquote ve all heard those stories, haven\rquote 
t we?) and many email apps will download attachments by default to a computer. If you\rquote re in a shared space or at work, it\rquote s best to keep any confidential and sensitive data away from email as much as possible.
\par }\pard\plain \ltrpar\s2\ql \li0\ri0\sl500\slmult0\keepn\widctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\outlinelevel1\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11800560 \rtlch\fcs1 \ab\ai\af1\afs28\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 
